#       1 (pt3+pt4)*cm, 
#       2 sqrt(pt3^2+pt4^2)*cm, 
#       3 mgg*cm,
#       4 cm*pt_photon
#       5 cm*pt_photon*sqrt((1+exp(-2*abs(y*)))/2)
# pt3 and pt4 are the transverse momentum of the two photons, mgg is 
# the invariant mass of them, y* = (y_photon-y_jet)/2
#
4
